column5: Yesterday Duane asked me to go fishing in his boat.  Duane did all the fishing and I was his net man. He went three for three.  Two on minnows and one on a yarn ball.
I think I might have seen you guys running around in that boat!  lol  I went two for two on brownies yesterday down there from shore.
nice pull He's got them in the boat so you must have been a good net man!
Stop that Doug.I'm not done with the ice and snow. Nice fish though.
Awesome Corvy    Good on you for netting them beauties
Yep that was the boat we saw.  Was a nice day to be out wasn't it?
Right on, looks like a productive day
